en_46560_0	Revised train fares are effective from today.
en_46560_1	The Sri Lanka Railway Service said that under the revision the minimum fare will not be changed for the first, second and third classes.
en_46560_2	However, the maximum distance that can be traveled with the minimum fare will be reduced from 9 kilometer to 7 kilometer.
en_46560_3	The train fares have been revised after a lapse of 10 years.
en_46560_4	There will also be change in the fee levied for season tickets along with the train fare revision.
en_46560_5	But the Sri Lanka Railway Service said that a change is not being effected to the percentage so far charged for season tickets.
en_46560_6	It further said that even after the revision that train fares are less than the bus fares.
